    "startTime": 320.0,
    "endTime": 320.5,
    "text": "Listen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.5,
    "endTime": 322.0,
    "text": "For a thousand years,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.0,
    "endTime": 327.5,
    "text": "I've only been thinking of keeping this hair silky, getting my hook, and being awesome again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.5,
    "endTime": 334.0,
    "text": "And it's not getting screwed up by a mortal who has no business inside of a monster cave, except— except..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.5,
    "endTime": 335.5,
    "text": "maybe his bait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.5,
    "endTime": 337.0,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.0,
    "endTime": 338.5,
    "text": "Wow!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.0,
    "endTime": 340.5,
    "text": "A shiny, glittery cave!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.0,
    "endTime": 345.5,
    "text": "And just like me, it is covered in sparkly treasure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.5,
    "endTime": 347.5,
    "text": "Sparkle, sparkle, sparkle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.5,
    "endTime": 348.5,
    "text": "You're not selling it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.5,
    "endTime": 349.5,
    "text": "This is stupid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.5,
    "endTime": 350.5,
    "text": "I'm just gonna walk up and get it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.5,
    "endTime": 352.5,
    "text": "You go up there, he will kill you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.5,
    "endTime": 353.5,
    "text": "Just stick to the plan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.0,
    "endTime": 355.5,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.5,
    "endTime": 357.5,
    "text": "When he shows up, keep him distracted."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.5,
    "endTime": 359.5,
    "text": "Make him talk about himself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.5,
    "endTime": 361.5,
    "text": "He loves playing hide-and-seek."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361.5,
    "endTime": 362.5,
    "text": "Make him talk about himself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.5,
    "endTime": 364.5,
    "text": "He loves bragging about how great he is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.5,
    "endTime": 366.5,
    "text": "You two must get along swell."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367.5,
    "endTime": 368.5,
    "text": "Not since I ripped off his leg."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.5,
    "endTime": 370.5,
