  {
    "startTime": 380.5,
    "endTime": 381.5,
    "text": "We're alive!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.5,
    "endTime": 384.5,
    "text": "Listen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 384.5,
    "endTime": 387.5,
    "text": "I, uh, appreciate what you did down there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.5,
    "endTime": 388.5,
    "text": "Took guts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.5,
    "endTime": 390.5,
    "text": "But, uh,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.5,
    "endTime": 391.5,
    "text": "I'm sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 391.5,
    "endTime": 395.5,
    "text": "I'm trying to be sincere, for once, and it feels like you're distracted."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.5,
    "endTime": 396.5,
    "text": "No! No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 396.5,
    "endTime": 397.5,
    "text": "No way!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397.5,
    "endTime": 398.5,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.5,
    "endTime": 399.5,
    "text": "Because you're looking at me like I have a—"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.5,
    "endTime": 403.5,
    "text": "Shark head."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.5,
    "endTime": 404.5,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405.5,
    "endTime": 406.5,
    "text": "Do you have a shark head?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 406.5,
    "endTime": 407.5,
    "text": "Because I—"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.5,
    "endTime": 416.5,
    "text": "Look, the point is, for a little girl, child, thing, whatever, who had no business being down there, you did me a solid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 416.5,
    "endTime": 418.5,
    "text": "But you also almost died."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 418.5,
    "endTime": 420.5,
    "text": "And I couldn't even beat the dumb crab."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 420.5,
    "endTime": 424.5,
    "text": "So chances of beating Taka are bupkis."
